dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:100,000 scale maps of Tanimbar Islands, titled 'Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Taninbaru Shotō jūmanbun no ichi zu -- Taninbaru Shotō jūmanbun no ichi zu -- 空中寫真測圖要圖タニンバル諸島十万分一圖 -- タニンバル諸島十万分一圖/Kūchū shashin sokuzu yōzu Taninbaru Shotō jūmanbun no ichi zu.' To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
